title: Keras U-Net starter - LB 0.277
description: IntroHello! This rather quick and dirty kernel shows how to get started on segmenting nuclei using a neural network in Keras. The architecture used is the so-called U-Net, which is very common for image segmentation problems such as this. I believe they also have a tendency to work quite well even on small datasets. Let's get started importing everything we need!
